n-masculine/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> MASCULINE FEMININE 系列</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103607rMPWaERwlFfohNKt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.268182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708151036070iMar1hPZVYxdpmf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.245455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708151036151xlmk8Iwu6JoFqHQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.463636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103615ThKcuOIqyeZFDU5X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.381818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103630xKo5hyb3S47kP0Ww.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103630UHnqMFuzlZmfNcsC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103630B17xJNTYHdURLKpv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103631Cs7HNrBvO3IZWYcq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103631xnVsg06iPuXC3HML.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103632GTdloAyw7PUFxcgJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103632iSoXcTj27BDHy5KV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103632U5SzmYhG7u2j1WeR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017081510363229yZJFlcUSNr7swi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103636eQ1JcCPOy4RhtpnV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Miu Miu 最新发布的 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/miu-miu-changes-its-logo-in-latest-fall-winter-2017-handbags-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">My Miu 系列包包</a>中，破天荒地更改了 logo 设计，新设计在字母中间加入了白线，字体也变大了一些。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103654bdszqWN9R17BpSM6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103656RXsFS63fyIhKiW8C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103659h8JKbcTOrnwSoV0f.png\" data-ratio=\"1.166412\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>日本潮牌<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/08/14/mastermind-japan-fw17-collection/#slide-13\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Mastermind JAPAN 发布秋冬系列 lookbook</a>，一系列大骷髅头图案的棒球外套、hoodie、皮衣、衬衫和毛皮外套，暗黑气质呼之欲出。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103713QEeU2FHy3ioanBcP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103713XlN4V5IRyGvF378E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017081510371374qOsy5ulABho1ZP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103714GBdWwTK0Pe8nOVgj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708151037145veNRn78ajpyFBAl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103714o8WUPVOFpfXG7yKl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103719rC7nh4KiWt8aoElD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103718nmyvi8aCPbSQc6pr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708151037229DfamLsSQc61uCAb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103722u3CQxtqpKAycsmYF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103722HmweruzY0xMjyq6g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103723T2035kemfMygA4WZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>加拿大奢侈羽绒服品牌 <a href=\"https://gearpatrol.com/2017/08/14/canada-goose-knitwear-fall-17/#6\" rel=\"nofollow\">Canada Goose 推出了品牌首个针织系列</a>。该系列共包括 15 款男女装针织产品，售价在 295 美元至 650 美元之间，主要色调为黑色、海军蓝、灰色和墨绿色。现已登陆 Canada Goose 官网。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103735EwBN14XtADHzQ38k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103735kEBZdHS64rNFOeVM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708151037407zxN8AZYEU4KMG3p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103748NcXBihxRGgSW3qpZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103748J9dAoIROSsym5aH1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170815103752FWvBDr2ebt0ACIO7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.67